N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 479.14 - Applicability of this part

State Regulations

The provisions of this Part shall apply to all disciplinary
actions commenced upon or after the date of approval by the Governor in
accordance with subdivision 3 of section 215 of article 11 of the Executive Law
and to all disciplinary actions commenced prior to such effective date but
still pending on such date. Notes
